{"tid":1020272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"深水埗69歲婦人遭電單車撞低昏迷","createTime":"2019-02-13T13:24:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-13T13:26:42.000Z","uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a783a4b290172106f04b67727cc776b58511f3e4","tid":1020272,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T13:24:35.000Z","msg":"深水埗發生交通意外。今日(13日)下午約5時半，一名姓鄭(37歲)男子駕駛電單車，沿汝州街往西九龍中心方向行駛，至北河街交界時，一名姓梁(69歲)婦人橫過馬路，鐵騎士疑收掣不及，電單車把梁婦撞倒，她重傷倒地一度昏迷，途人見狀報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n救護員接報趕至，替梁婦急救後再送院搶救，其後回復清醒。鄭手腳擦傷，酒精呼氣測試為0度，其後亦由救護車送院治理。警方封鎖現場，現場遺下血漬，意外原因仍待進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190213/bkn-20190213180823506-0213_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190213%2Fbkn-20190213180823506-0213_00822_001.html&d=uNZXw00WsTXXX%2FAwV3JyES3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=ed6cc57d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190213/bkn-20190213180823506-0213_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a59da2aea60a45d64192095c49346b44f4c7c574","tid":1020272,"uid":85117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T13:26:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jEayXqa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjEayXqa.jpg&h=cc343ecc&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}